Emote Management System
==========================

This system allows for the addition, removal and suspension of
emotes on the "fly". Allowing you to manage emotes much easier
then manually manipulating files, rehashing, etc..


Commands of this system:
    eadd <emote>
    epromote <emote>
    edemote <emote>
    esuspend <emote>
    eupdate

    elist <pending/active/removed/all>


See also
  (eadd) (epromote) (edemote) (esuspend) (eupdate) (elist)

Note this system is used by ARCH+
